snippet.title: Super Mario Odyssey but I get Power Moons I missed (Wooded Kingdom)
snippet.description:
Super Mario Odyssey Power Moons first time playing/ going to all kingdoms getting all power moons in Super Mario Odyssey in the Wooded Kingdom/ Cascade Kingdom/ Moon Kingdom/ Bowser Kingdom/ Sand Kingdom and all Kingdoms Mario Odyssey before the MUSHROOM KINGDOM Super Mario Odyssey! Super Mario Odyssey is a fantastic Nintendo Switch game, hilarious Mario animations, amazing Mario captures, incredible secret levels, and visiting all moon pipes only made me appreicate the game Super Mario Odyssey even more, it's a masterpiece!

A little backstory: I just want to give a huge thank you to you for watching this video, it's because of you that I got to play this game and make this video. Super Mario Odyssey is a game that I've been wanting to play for years (just like Breath of the Wild and Minecraft, hopefully I can finish Minecraft and start Breath of the Wild soon!), and it's because my YouTube channel has been doing so well that I got to finally give this game a try! Thank you so much for watching, and thank you so much for all of the support!

FULL SUPER MARIO ODYSSEY PLAYTHROUGH PLAYLIST: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7MOs6WUyXHY&list=PLhtPEroyK1P4YJ-F89ilH4ZnBuiaEwRt0
